{"tid":1753552,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【機密流出】林鄭訪京，棋子走錯！恐「被貪污」！","createTime":"2019-11-25T03:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T03:57:46.000Z","uid":184099,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"721bb8a3bc5eb466a334211bb49b9a156918c96b","tid":1753552,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:23:48.000Z","msg":"據紅二代內部消息指，先<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>前林鄭月娥在11月5日晚上由上海突然轉到北京，直接被國家主席習近平訓話。<br />\n<br />\n表面看似國家主席習近平大力支持林鄭月娥，實際是希望林鄭月娥能把香港的事情搞得「乾乾淨淨」，以便讓國家專心打貿易戰。<strong>甚至威脅林鄭月娥如果搞不到，就全面被中國封鎖，世世代代納入中國黑名單。</strong><br />\n<br />\n而林鄭月娥表示，會全力協助11月24日建制派選舉，打沉泛民派。懇求國家主席習近平再給她一個機會，絕對有信心。<br />\n<br />\n而現實證明，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即使「協助」建制派選舉，亦不敵強大的民意</span></strong>。但側面看，紅二代甚至中共高層內部都開始動搖，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">深信香港高層內部「搞的鬼」</span></strong>，不可能每次都把棋子走錯！<br />\n<br />\n而更可怕的是，林鄭月娥在退任後將會「被貪污」，跟一向不聽中央說話的曾蔭權下場一樣！"},{"pid":"33fecce294f3aa94c7e7f3ab7a5c62235fef6c85","tid":1753552,"uid":292384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"巴大幾時找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e0930ea3842ca7b2a9339d1dfb6c41755fd705","tid":1753552,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33fecce294f3aa94c7e7f3ab7a5c62235fef6c85","tid":1753552,"uid":292384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"巴大幾時找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1751635/page/8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1751635/page/8</a>"},{"pid":"9419544aee214703babfc7a9b2a17a3e6f3d8cf5","tid":1753552,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/